page_title: Best practices for using Azure OpenAI On Your Data
page_description: Learn about the best practices when using Azure OpenAI On Your data.
chunk_content: InferencingThis is the stage where users chat with their data using a studio, deployed webapp, or direct API calls. In this stage users are able to set various model parameters (such as `temperature`, or `top_P` ) and system parameters such as `strictness`, and `topNDocuments`.
